OL,6,FThe national minimum wage ` which
OL,7,Fcovers those aged 21 or under ` will
OL,8,Fgo up to #10 an hour for 18 to 20-year-
OL,9,Folds, a 16.3% rise, and to #7.55 for
OL,10,F16 and 17-year-olds, an 18% increase.
OL,12,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak told
OL,13,Fthe PA news agency: "This increase
OL,14,Fwill make a real difference to the
OL,15,Flowest paid in this country at a time
OL,16,Fwhen one in six are skipping meals to
OL,17,Fget by.
